  "name": "Life's Last Breath",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>The twin serrated blades of this legendary rhoka sword are dull black and constantly drip with blood. <em>Life's Last Breath</em> is said to have been forged centuries ago for an unknown urdefhan general and has since fallen into the hands of countless other powerful urdefhan warlords.</p>\n<p><em>Life's Last Breath</em> is a <em>+3 greater striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.gmMrJREf4JSHd2dZ]{Unholy} @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.fo6Yhq5mbQXsnZs0]{Wounding} rhoka sword</em> with the following special abilities.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">R</span> command</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You successfully Strike a creature with <em>Life's Last Breath</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast a 9th-level <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.DCQHaLrYXMI37dvW]{Paralyze}</em> spell on the target.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">R</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You successfully Strike a creature with <em>Life's Last Breath</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The target must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:38] or take @Damage[4d6[void]] damage; you gain an equal amount of temporary Hit Points that last 1 minute.</p>"
    },
